Content:: Reference: European Commission, Joint Research Centre (EC-JRC)/Netherlands Environmental Assessment Agency (PBL). Emissions Database for Global Atmospheric Research (EDGAR), release EDGAR v7.0_GHG (1970 - 2021) of September 2022. For the energy related sectors the activity data are mainly based on IEA data from IEA (2021) World Energy Balances, www.iea.org/statistics, All rights reserved, as modified by Joint Research Centre, European Commission.
